Rating: 3
This chili was great other than one main thing. The chili sauce was too dominant. Instead of enhancing the chili, it overpowered it a bit too much. I've reduced the amt. to 1/4 C. on my recipe for next time. Also I added 2 jalapenos without any seeds or pith. It was just the right heat. Not too hot and not too mild. Other than the chili sauce, the chili was quite good. I will most definitely make this again. I'll have to write another review then. DO try this recipe. It is nice and hearty. Be sure to make cornbread in an iron skillet to go with it. Perfect combo!

