Rating: 4
Great and easy. I am sure the recipe is excellent as is. However, I did add some sliced sun dried tomatos. I used Ground Elk instead of beef (Elk is extreemily low in fat and high in protien - Elk meat is easy to burn,so use a little olive oil when browning). I like my chili a little more soupy and so added one 12 ounce dark beer.

