Rating: 4
I made this vegetarien. I cut out the meat, and I subtituted beef broth with vegetable broth. I also tossed in 1/2 cup of fresh cilantro, 1/4 cup of fresh basil, 1 tsp of hot pepper flakes. I added an extra potato, I threw in a cup of frozen corn and I added 3 bell peppers. Half a bottle of spaghetti sauce to thicken things up. The whole family loved this-- even though they are all meat eaters. VERY satisfying, it had a nice bite to it.

